# Edit this file to introduce tasks to be run by cron.
# 
# Each task to run has to be defined through a single line
# indicating with different fields when the task will be run
# and what command to run for the task
# 
# To define the time you can provide concrete values for
# minute (m), hour (h), day of month (dom), month (mon),
# and day of week (dow) or use '*' in these fields (for 'any').
# 
# Notice that tasks will be started based on the cron's system
# daemon's notion of time and timezones.
# 
# Output of the crontab jobs (including errors) is sent through
# email to the user the crontab file belongs to (unless redirected).
# 
# For example, you can run a backup of all your user accounts
# at 5 a.m every week with:
# 0 5 * * 1 tar -zcf /var/backups/home.tgz /home/
# 
# For more information see the manual pages of crontab(5) and cron(8)
# 
# m h  dom mon dow   command
0 4 * * * python3 /home/furycom/kb_maintenance.py >> /home/furycom/logs/kb_maintenance.log 2>&1
# DESACTIVE 2026-02-22 session72 # 30 4 * * * python3 /home/furycom/roadmap_extractor.py --hours 26 >> /home/furycom/logs/roadmap_extractor.log 2>&1.log 2>&1
*/5 * * * * bash /home/furycom/inbox_watcher.sh >> /home/furycom/logs/inbox_watcher.log 2>&1
0 * * * * python3 /home/furycom/sync_homelab_hub.py >> /tmp/sync_homelab_hub.log 2>&1
*/5 * * * * /home/furycom/bruce_watchdog.sh >> /home/furycom/logs/watchdog.log 2>&1
0 2 1 * * python3 /home/furycom/bruce_monthly_review.py >> /home/furycom/logs/monthly_review.log 2>&1
0 4 * * 0 /usr/bin/python3 /home/furycom/trivy_scan_weekly.py >> /home/furycom/logs/trivy_scan.log 2>&1
0 3 1 * * python3 /home/furycom/bruce_quality_review.py >> /home/furycom/logs/quality_review.log 2>&1
0 4 * * 0 . /home/furycom/.bookstack_env && python3 /home/furycom/bookstack_sync.py >> /home/furycom/logs/bookstack_sync.log 2>&1
0 5 * * * /home/furycom/pulse_sync_cron.sh >> /home/furycom/logs/pulse_sync_cron.log 2>&1
15 * * * * python3 /home/furycom/bruce_alert_dispatcher.py >> /home/furycom/logs/alert_dispatcher.log 2>&1
*/5 * * * * /home/furycom/dspy_cron_watchdog_disabled.sh
